components:
  schemas:
    tmp0:
      properties:
        nets: {type: string}
        status: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp1:
      properties:
        act: {type: string}
        acth: {type: string}
        as: {type: string}
        asdesc: {type: string}
        asname: {type: string}
        bgproute: {type: string}
        city: {type: string}
        country: {type: string}
        pas: {type: string}
        pash: {type: string}
        routedesc: {type: string}
        status: {type: string}
        whoisdesc: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp2:
      properties:
        final_results: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp3:
      properties:
        results_reverse: {type: string}
      type: object
  securitySchemes: {}
info:
  contact: {email: frikky@shuffler.io, name: '@frikkylikeme', url: 'https://twitter.com/frikkylikeme'}
  description: Automated generation of Robtex Robtex
  title: Robtex Robtex
  version: 1.0.0
  x-logo: data:image/png;base64,
openapi: 3.0.2
paths:
  tmp0:
    post:
      description: Retrieve an array of networks related to a specific AS number
      parameters:
      - description: AS Number
        example: '1234'
        in: body
        name: AS Number
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp0'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Robtex AS Query
  tmp1:
    post:
      description: Retrieve the current forward and reverse of an ip address
      parameters:
      - description: IP Address
        example: 192.168.1.1
        in: query
        name: IP Address
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp1'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Robtex IP Query
  tmp2:
    post:
      description: ' Passive DNS forward'
      parameters:
      - description: PDNS Forward URL
        example: example.com
        in: query
        name: PDNS Forward URL
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp2'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Robtex PDNS Forward
  tmp3:
    post:
      description: ' Passive DNS reverse'
      parameters:
      - description: PDNS Reverse IP Address
        example: 192.168.1.1
        in: query
        name: PDNS Reverse IP Address
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp3'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Robtex PDNS Reverse
tags:
- {name: Investigation}
